# TBA4256 – 3D Digital Modelling  
Assignments 1 & 2  

This repository contains scripts for **Assignment 1** and **Assignment 2** in the course *TBA4256 – 3D Digital Modelling*.  
Both assignments involve processing of point cloud data using **Open3D**, **NumPy**, and **LasPy**.

---

## Installation

Before running any of the scripts, make sure you have Python 3.10 or newer installed.  
Then create a virtual environment and install all dependencies from `requirements.txt`.

```bash
# Create and activate virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate        # (Windows)
# source venv/bin/activate   # (Mac/Linux)

# Upgrade pip and install dependencies
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
